          "reviewBody": "As for me , this is not the best but the worst .\nMost of the teachers will not be approachable and kind of controlling . I studied here and I heard from some of my juniors that  they are closing the gates for the students who came late , manners and discipline matter but not this much , shutting the gates and making them stand there for the whole prayer , in the road!!! . And if you think your past schools doesn't care about your hairstyle so this School will also not care about it , you're wrong the pt teachers here will tear you image apart and will definitely insult you IN front of everyone and doesn't care about your feelings . In here teachers aren't friendly , some doesn't even care to see you exist , But there were some good teachers but not now . I found out that most of the reviews here are from the teachers in administration , I recognized some of them and mostly their names . So don't believe these 5 star reviews . This school is mostly money minded . For them money matters not education . I wish I could have gone to good school that supports me and helped me with my studies . This school is one of my nightmares . if you want your child to be happy and all don't get them in to this school they will mess up your kids mind and your money will be going in to their films . !!!! DON'T GET ADDMISSION IN THIS SCHOOL!!!!!!!!!!",
